WEBVTT

00:02:50.169 --> 00:02:51.604
VT! Your shift's up?

00:02:51.938 --> 00:02:53.773
Finally. How about you?

00:02:54.474 --> 00:02:56.342
I'm off to Europa now.

00:02:56.476 --> 00:02:59.479
-That's got pretty good pay.
-It's nothing compared to yours.

00:02:59.546 --> 00:03:02.782
I heard you made a round-trip
from here to Venus in four days?

00:03:03.516 --> 00:03:05.952
-Three days.
-See what I mean?

00:03:06.219 --> 00:03:07.654
Anyway, take it easy.

00:03:08.187 --> 00:03:09.289
Thanks.

00:03:09.689 --> 00:03:10.557
Oh yeah, I forgot.

00:03:11.891 --> 00:03:12.892
VT!

00:03:15.395 --> 00:03:16.596
You're still not giving up?

00:03:16.663 --> 00:03:20.400
Of course not!
How much do you think I lent you?

00:03:21.301 --> 00:03:22.535
Suit yourself.

00:03:24.404 --> 00:03:27.874
All right. You only get one shot,
and you get no clues.

00:03:28.241 --> 00:03:31.511
Yeah! VT, your name is...

00:03:32.211 --> 00:03:33.513
Vivian Tillana.

00:03:35.648 --> 00:03:36.516
Nope!

00:03:36.583 --> 00:03:37.483
Oh, man...

00:03:37.917 --> 00:03:39.452
This is a bad omen.

00:03:39.919 --> 00:03:41.521
You be careful now.

00:03:43.790 --> 00:03:47.260
{\an8}Yeah, you know that Cock-Eye guy
that was worth 8 million the other day?

00:03:47.327 --> 00:03:49.562
{\an8}Believe it or not,
I was the one who caught him!

00:03:49.629 --> 00:03:53.733
What do you mean, the other day?
That was 10 years ago, you old geezer!

00:03:54.467 --> 00:03:59.005
What are you saying, you young'uns!
I was the one that taught Telpsicorei!

00:03:59.272 --> 00:04:00.940
You mean the legendary bounty hunter?

00:04:01.007 --> 00:04:05.511
Every bounty cowered in fear
just at the mention of his name.

00:04:05.578 --> 00:04:07.280
Oh, Everyone knows that.

00:04:17.824 --> 00:04:18.891
Hey, Zeros.

00:04:18.992 --> 00:04:21.728
Welcome, VT. The usual?

00:04:21.794 --> 00:04:22.695
Yeah.

00:04:22.762 --> 00:04:25.632
What's going on today?
The place is usually empty.

00:04:25.832 --> 00:04:27.267
Oh, this?

00:04:27.600 --> 00:04:31.471
Apparently a bounty named Decker
is gonna pass by around here.

00:04:31.537 --> 00:04:33.439
They're all bounty hunters.

00:04:34.974 --> 00:04:37.844
No wonder they all look so cheap.

00:04:38.511 --> 00:04:40.613
What was that about
"top secret" information?

00:04:40.680 --> 00:04:43.016
This place is full of our kind.

00:04:43.616 --> 00:04:46.352
And I got a hangover today, too.

00:04:47.320 --> 00:04:51.824
Besides, we don't know the face.
The only clue is a dragon-shaped tattoo.

00:04:52.592 --> 00:04:53.726
Faye?

00:04:54.494 --> 00:04:56.562
Like that place is gonna be any better.

00:04:56.629 --> 00:04:57.497
WOODY'S P

00:04:57.964 --> 00:04:59.565
<i>Welcome to Woody's!</i>

00:04:59.932 --> 00:05:02.969
<i>Right now, all of our friends who</i>
<i>are celebrating their birthdays</i>

00:05:03.036 --> 00:05:05.905
<i>can get their pictures taken</i>
<i>with Mackey and Mannie!</i>

00:05:06.572 --> 00:05:09.575
<i>Moms and Dads, please tell your server!</i>

00:05:16.816 --> 00:05:17.884
Hi.

00:05:19.585 --> 00:05:21.854
What do you want? You wanna get some?

00:05:21.921 --> 00:05:25.458
I'd rather be the one that gives some.

00:05:25.525 --> 00:05:27.427
I'm fine with that.

00:05:27.560 --> 00:05:29.362
Hands in the air, Decker!

00:05:33.866 --> 00:05:36.903
-Don't be so difficult!
-Just get the hell over here.

00:05:36.969 --> 00:05:38.371
But I have work!

00:05:38.438 --> 00:05:40.006
Just make yourself comfortable!

00:05:40.073 --> 00:05:40.940
Git!

00:05:41.641 --> 00:05:42.975
Please, stop.

00:05:43.042 --> 00:05:44.644
I'll give you a good time.

00:05:45.778 --> 00:05:46.813
Stop!

00:05:46.879 --> 00:05:48.114
Someone!

00:05:49.682 --> 00:05:50.683
What the hell are you?

00:05:50.750 --> 00:05:51.884
VT!

00:05:53.419 --> 00:05:58.658
So, it's a bounty hunter's job to chase
a woman's ass instead of a bounty?

00:05:59.392 --> 00:06:01.728
Sorry, but this is my job.

00:06:02.095 --> 00:06:04.063
-What...
-Don't play dumb with me.

00:06:04.630 --> 00:06:06.766
That dragon-shaped tattoo
is unmistakable proof.

00:06:08.701 --> 00:06:10.603
You got the wrong man.

00:06:10.703 --> 00:06:11.871
Hey, you over there!

00:06:12.505 --> 00:06:13.840
Call the police!

00:06:14.040 --> 00:06:16.676
Tell them I caught Decker the bounty!

00:06:32.759 --> 00:06:33.860
This is?

00:06:34.761 --> 00:06:36.028
Yakkun, the eight-eyed eel.

00:06:36.896 --> 00:06:38.698
Don't be so mistakable!

00:06:53.479 --> 00:06:54.147
Why you!

00:07:13.800 --> 00:07:14.767
You!

00:07:15.735 --> 00:07:16.803
VT!

00:07:18.171 --> 00:07:20.773
You're wearing my patience thin.

00:07:24.510 --> 00:07:25.978
What the hell are you?

00:07:26.045 --> 00:07:29.148
Grudges over lost food
aren't a pretty sight!

00:07:30.950 --> 00:07:33.085
Shit, let's get this guy too!

00:07:56.209 --> 00:07:57.076
Found him!

00:08:11.023 --> 00:08:12.925
Shit, I'll get you back for this!

00:08:14.560 --> 00:08:16.596
Just kidding.

00:08:16.662 --> 00:08:18.998
Forget about us!

00:08:26.839 --> 00:08:28.975
My 12 million...

00:08:31.277 --> 00:08:35.781
Really. Bounty hunters
are all stupid scum.

00:08:36.516 --> 00:08:38.117
-You think so?
-Yeah!

00:08:38.184 --> 00:08:42.688
As far as I know, they're all
living their lives by gambling.

00:08:43.623 --> 00:08:45.224
Well, maybe so.

00:08:46.192 --> 00:08:48.828
Come over here. I'll treat you to a drink.

00:08:53.866 --> 00:08:57.103
What? Bean sprouts are good for you!

00:08:59.572 --> 00:09:03.175
Give me a break! That's all we have!

00:09:03.576 --> 00:09:04.577
Oh! Here it comes!

00:09:05.044 --> 00:09:07.113
Oh, it's you, Faye. That was quick.

00:09:08.648 --> 00:09:09.315
What!?

00:09:10.650 --> 00:09:13.019
But that sure is a disgusting drink.

00:09:13.619 --> 00:09:15.054
It's a prairie oyster.

00:09:15.321 --> 00:09:16.622
It's good for hangovers.

00:09:22.128 --> 00:09:24.997
You're the second person I've met
that drinks that stuff.

00:09:25.731 --> 00:09:26.599
And the first one?

00:09:27.867 --> 00:09:29.035
My husband.

00:09:29.802 --> 00:09:30.903
VT!

00:09:31.337 --> 00:09:33.839
-We'll get it this time.
-The money!

00:09:34.774 --> 00:09:35.942
Once for the three of you?

00:09:36.208 --> 00:09:37.176
Yeah!

00:09:37.243 --> 00:09:38.277
Suit yourself.

00:09:40.780 --> 00:09:42.315
All right! Here we go!

00:09:43.149 --> 00:09:45.718
VT, your name is...

00:09:46.285 --> 00:09:48.087
I think Adrienne is good.

00:09:50.189 --> 00:09:51.757
That doesn't start with a V.

00:09:51.824 --> 00:09:55.695
That's why I said we should stick
with Leticia!

00:09:55.828 --> 00:09:56.762
You think so?

00:09:56.829 --> 00:09:59.165
I can have that money
if I guess your name?

00:09:59.865 --> 00:10:00.833
Yeah.

00:10:01.067 --> 00:10:03.302
I don't remember who started it...

00:10:04.070 --> 00:10:06.138
but it kept piling up and here we are now.

00:10:06.906 --> 00:10:07.974
Can I try, too?

00:10:09.976 --> 00:10:11.077
<i>Spike! It's me!</i>

00:10:11.143 --> 00:10:12.912
<i>Faye let Decker get away.</i>

00:10:13.646 --> 00:10:14.680
<i>Go after him now.</i>

00:10:19.785 --> 00:10:21.020
Spike!

00:10:21.253 --> 00:10:22.888
Get lost!

00:10:23.623 --> 00:10:24.991
Idiotic lying scum!

00:10:25.625 --> 00:10:26.659
I ain't treating you!

00:10:31.230 --> 00:10:33.299
No, Spike!

00:10:37.103 --> 00:10:38.771
Oh, my.

00:10:40.706 --> 00:10:44.310
{\an8}Oh, this, those whatchamacallit brothers
did this before they took off.

00:10:45.111 --> 00:10:46.112
And you were watching?

00:10:49.315 --> 00:10:51.050
Why didn't you tell me?

00:10:51.817 --> 00:10:54.020
What? I just told you right now!

00:11:01.260 --> 00:11:02.128
What?

00:11:09.001 --> 00:11:11.003
Hey, VT... going home?

00:11:11.070 --> 00:11:13.139
Got a problem with that?
Come on, Zeros.

00:11:19.745 --> 00:11:21.781
-And what are you doing?
-Hitchhiking.

00:11:22.715 --> 00:11:24.784
My machine was vandalized.

00:11:25.751 --> 00:11:28.020
You're really a stupid...

00:11:28.087 --> 00:11:31.424
Lying, shameless scum
of a bounty hunter?

00:11:31.690 --> 00:11:33.159
If you don't stop with all this...

00:11:43.002 --> 00:11:43.969
Follow me.

00:11:44.870 --> 00:11:46.338
Can I bring someone with me?

00:11:53.946 --> 00:11:56.282
Man! How many times
do I have to say the same thing?

00:11:56.348 --> 00:11:59.118
He was short, bald,
wearing glasses and a Sarasvati.

00:11:59.185 --> 00:12:00.853
Huh? What?

00:12:00.920 --> 00:12:02.088
I just said...

00:12:03.889 --> 00:12:06.292
Really! Can you turn
that shit-loud noise off?

00:12:06.926 --> 00:12:09.495
They say, "When in Rome,
do as the Romans do."

00:12:11.330 --> 00:12:13.332
And it's not shit-loud noise.

00:12:13.933 --> 00:12:15.935
It's called heavy metal!

00:12:28.948 --> 00:12:31.383
Really, both of you together...

00:12:31.984 --> 00:12:34.420
Who do you think is going
to repair these?

00:12:36.989 --> 00:12:40.159
What the hell am I supposed to do
with that little bit of information?

00:12:40.226 --> 00:12:43.762
How many bald people with glasses
do you think there are in this universe?

00:12:43.829 --> 00:12:46.432
So I said, bald, short, with glasses...

00:12:46.765 --> 00:12:50.136
and driving a gaudy truck
with Sarasvati painted on it!

00:12:53.038 --> 00:12:54.039
Yeah?

00:12:54.240 --> 00:12:55.808
<i>That you, VT?</i>

00:12:55.875 --> 00:12:57.376
Oh, Otto. What's up?

00:12:57.443 --> 00:12:59.378
<i>I got into a hit-and-run.</i>

00:13:00.913 --> 00:13:04.049
<i>The guy cut in line at the gate entrance,</i>
<i>rammed me, and took off!</i>

00:13:04.517 --> 00:13:07.820
<i>Shit, I gotta make him pay for repairs!</i>

00:13:07.920 --> 00:13:09.822
<i>Tell me if you see him!</i>

00:13:10.256 --> 00:13:11.190
<i>Anything specific?</i>

00:13:11.457 --> 00:13:12.892
Let's see.

00:13:13.058 --> 00:13:16.195
There was some oriental
goddess drawn on...

00:13:16.362 --> 00:13:18.864
<i>Wait a minute! Was it Sarasvati?</i>

00:13:19.131 --> 00:13:22.201
Oh yeah, her. How'd you know?

00:13:23.369 --> 00:13:24.236
Zeros.

00:13:27.206 --> 00:13:29.842
<i>Breaker one-nine, Breaker one-nine.</i>

00:13:29.909 --> 00:13:31.544
<i>To all truckers in the asteroid belt.</i>

00:13:31.810 --> 00:13:33.546
<i>This is Heavy Metal Queen.</i>

00:13:33.846 --> 00:13:38.350
<i>Ring me up if you see a gaudy truck</i>
<i>with Sarasvati painted on it. Thanks.</i>

00:13:38.951 --> 00:13:41.253
{\an8}<i>VT, this is Love Machine.</i>

00:13:41.353 --> 00:13:42.955
{\an8}<i>What's up with it?</i>

00:13:43.022 --> 00:13:45.057
<i>Some guy you were chasing ran away?</i>

00:13:45.124 --> 00:13:46.225
<i>Something like that.</i>

00:13:46.825 --> 00:13:49.528
I haven't seen the guy,
but I'll be on the lookout.

00:13:49.995 --> 00:13:51.030
<i>Thanks. It'll help.</i>

00:13:52.031 --> 00:13:55.434
This is Sneaky Snake.
Did you say it was a painting of a clown?

00:13:56.035 --> 00:13:56.902
<i>Nope.</i>

00:13:56.969 --> 00:13:59.538
<i>This is Spider Mike,</i>
<i>Black Panther of Jupiter.</i>

00:13:59.972 --> 00:14:04.276
<i>VT, I've never met you but I hear lots</i>
<i>of rumors about the Heavy Metal Queen.</i>

00:14:04.910 --> 00:14:06.612
Thanks for the compliment. So, any info?

00:14:07.446 --> 00:14:10.516
I passed by someone like the one you're
looking for 10 minutes ago.

00:14:10.583 --> 00:14:12.618
It was around the Linus mines.

00:14:13.586 --> 00:14:14.520
<i>That help?</i>

00:14:15.387 --> 00:14:17.223
Thanks, I'll owe you one.

00:14:25.231 --> 00:14:27.967
I gotta exchange this, too.

00:14:41.380 --> 00:14:42.882
There he is!

00:14:52.291 --> 00:14:54.126
Trying to throw me off his trail.

00:14:56.929 --> 00:14:58.230
Maybe in the next century!

00:15:09.341 --> 00:15:13.245
Hey, is the stupid, lying, shameless
scum of a bounty hunter around?

00:15:13.646 --> 00:15:15.414
What!? The Linus mines!?

00:15:15.481 --> 00:15:17.983
-You're being reckless!
<i>-What did you say?</i>

00:15:18.384 --> 00:15:19.952
Stay away from Decker!

00:15:20.019 --> 00:15:21.553
His cargo is dangerous!

00:15:22.087 --> 00:15:23.022
Hey!

00:15:26.926 --> 00:15:30.429
Wait! I called first dibs on Decker!

00:15:38.938 --> 00:15:41.607
What is this? Really?
Do I have to put this silly thing on?

00:15:42.207 --> 00:15:45.010
I would've preferred that it was
your loud mouth that broke.

00:15:45.511 --> 00:15:46.578
I heard that.

00:15:47.146 --> 00:15:48.447
I'm going out, Jet!

00:15:48.948 --> 00:15:52.017
Spike, the main gun on that thing
isn't fixed yet!

00:16:27.086 --> 00:16:28.354
Nice try, buddy.

00:16:51.510 --> 00:16:54.613
What is this? Isn't this a little risky?

00:16:55.080 --> 00:16:56.215
This way!

00:17:07.259 --> 00:17:09.161
My 12 million...

00:17:14.767 --> 00:17:16.368
<i>Hey, are you alive?</i>

00:17:16.435 --> 00:17:17.669
<i>If you hear me, answer!</i>

00:17:18.637 --> 00:17:21.440
<i>I'm fine. It takes more</i>
<i>than that to kill me.</i>

00:17:21.640 --> 00:17:22.574
We gotta run. Now!

00:17:23.509 --> 00:17:25.210
<i>Decker was a master of explosives.</i>

00:17:25.411 --> 00:17:28.380
<i>He's currently hauling the solid nitro</i>
<i>he was making deals with.</i>

00:17:30.616 --> 00:17:33.685
All of it? That's enough to blow up
this entire asteroid!

00:17:34.319 --> 00:17:36.355
<i>On top of it,</i>
<i>this place was an excel mine.</i>

00:17:36.622 --> 00:17:39.458
<i>The reactors have been randomly</i>
<i>exploding for a while now.</i>

00:17:43.462 --> 00:17:45.497
We gotta get this truck out of here.

00:18:07.186 --> 00:18:09.121
<i>How much further is the exit?</i>

00:18:09.188 --> 00:18:10.289
<i>A little further.</i>

00:18:10.589 --> 00:18:11.824
<i>Twenty degrees to the left.</i>

00:18:19.765 --> 00:18:21.166
There, the exit.

00:18:27.372 --> 00:18:28.373
No good.

00:18:28.774 --> 00:18:29.641
Behind us!

00:18:33.312 --> 00:18:34.179
No! In front!

00:18:38.117 --> 00:18:40.452
<i>What's with that?</i>
<i>That's nowhere near enough!</i>

00:18:40.552 --> 00:18:41.753
My main gun is busted!

00:18:42.221 --> 00:18:43.188
This is all I got!

00:18:43.255 --> 00:18:45.624
<i>And this is all I have!</i>

00:18:46.158 --> 00:18:48.460
What are we gonna do?
Isn't there another way?

00:18:48.727 --> 00:18:50.195
<i>Yeah, there is.</i>

00:18:50.796 --> 00:18:53.699
There's a ton of it in
the truck behind us!

00:18:59.671 --> 00:19:00.806
<i>I don't like this.</i>

00:19:01.406 --> 00:19:03.642
<i>I'm not one for delicate operations</i>
<i>like this!</i>

00:19:03.709 --> 00:19:05.644
Quit whining.

00:19:06.178 --> 00:19:07.246
Let's hit it big!

00:19:13.252 --> 00:19:15.320
<i>Yeah, now grab one.</i>

00:19:15.521 --> 00:19:17.289
That's easy for you to say.

00:19:21.360 --> 00:19:23.195
<i>Something is leaking.</i>

00:19:23.262 --> 00:19:24.630
<i>That's probably the stabilizer.</i>

00:19:24.696 --> 00:19:25.697
<i>That means...</i>

00:19:26.365 --> 00:19:28.367
<i>-Touch-sensitive.</i>
<i>-Wait a sec!</i>

00:19:33.172 --> 00:19:35.240
<i>At worst, you screw up and die.</i>

00:19:41.246 --> 00:19:44.283
<i>I got one.</i>
<i>What do you want to do with it?</i>

00:19:45.517 --> 00:19:49.421
<i>This pod will shoot towards the exit</i>
<i>and self-destruct in 40 seconds.</i>

00:19:50.522 --> 00:19:53.725
<i>So, get that thing in this pod</i>
<i>within 40 seconds.</i>

00:19:54.526 --> 00:19:55.761
What are you going to do?

00:19:56.395 --> 00:19:57.429
I'm gonna do... this.

00:20:10.943 --> 00:20:12.678
Zeros, we're opening the hatch!

00:20:48.780 --> 00:20:49.681
Bingo!

00:21:13.705 --> 00:21:14.673
It's clear!

00:21:32.057 --> 00:21:33.492
This sucks.

00:21:45.737 --> 00:21:46.638
Really...

00:21:51.043 --> 00:21:54.846
Thanks for the help, Victoria Telpsicorei.

00:21:55.847 --> 00:21:57.482
And give your husband my thanks.

00:21:57.949 --> 00:21:59.851
I figured out your name because of this.

00:22:01.887 --> 00:22:04.456
Unless you're a hermit,
everyone knows about him.

00:22:05.090 --> 00:22:08.827
{\an8}About the legendary bounty hunter,
Telpsicorei.

00:22:11.830 --> 00:22:13.832
It will be a while.

00:22:15.100 --> 00:22:17.869
My husband's working in Heaven right now.

00:22:18.470 --> 00:22:19.538
I see.

00:22:22.407 --> 00:22:23.809
Give the rest to your husband.

00:22:24.409 --> 00:22:26.378
I'm sure he's suffering from a hangover.

00:22:28.046 --> 00:22:30.082
So, I'll treat him to a prairie oyster.

00:24:12.617 --> 00:24:14.986
<i>Once in a while,</i>
<i>I'll do the preview by myself.</i>

00:24:15.587 --> 00:24:17.589
<i>I'm Jet Black, 36 years old.</i>

00:24:18.123 --> 00:24:21.092
<i>I'm often told that I don't look 36...</i>

00:24:21.193 --> 00:24:24.863
<i>but you shouldn't judge people by</i>
<i>their looks or how much hair they have.</i>

00:24:24.930 --> 00:24:27.065
<i>Things are never what they seem to be.</i>

00:24:27.132 --> 00:24:31.837
<i>The next episode is like that, too.</i>
<i>A fairy tale that seems very unlike Bebop.</i>

00:24:32.237 --> 00:24:34.806
<i>Next episode: Waltz for Venus.</i>

00:24:35.207 --> 00:24:37.242
<i>Stuff like this is good once in a while.</i>

